title: 820-00138 no power no green light
message:

and pp20v_dcin_fuse - 16.7V

title: 820-00138 no power no green light
message: [USER="461"]Gurmon[/USER] Great News replaced R7020 and machine fired right up :D:D. everything seems to be working as should however the machine does appear to be running rather slugish. Has anyone come across such an issue after water damage.

title: 820-00138 no power no green light
